---
// Custom Plans Landing Page
---
<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Custom Gym Plans — BuffBook</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Get a handcrafted, science-based gym plan tailored exactly to your goals, body, and experience level."
    />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <style>
      *, *::before, *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      :root {
        --gold: #f7c800;
        --gold-dim: #b38e00;
        --bg: #080808;
        --bg-card: #111111;
        --bg-card-hover: #181818;
        --border: #222222;
        --text: #e8e8e8;
        --text-muted: #888888;
        --radius: 8px;
      }
      body {
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
      }
      
      nav {
        position: fixed;
        top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
        z-index: 100;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
        height: 60px;
        background: rgba(8, 8, 8, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      }
      .nav-logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.4rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: var(--gold);
      }
      .nav-logo svg {
        width: 24px; height: 24px; fill: var(--gold);
      }

      .hero {
        min-height: 90vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 6rem clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem) 4rem;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .hero::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 60% at 50% 40%, rgba(247, 200, 0, 0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }
      .hero-eyebrow {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.2em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.6rem;
      }
      .hero-eyebrow::before, .hero-eyebrow::after {
        content: "";
        width: 2rem; height: 1px;
        background: var(--gold);
        opacity: 0.5;
      }
      .hero h1 {
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
        line-height: 0.95;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        color: #fff;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        max-width: 900px;
      }
      .hero h1 span { color: var(--gold); }
      .hero-sub {
        font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.2rem);
        color: var(--text-muted);
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        background: var(--gold);
        color: #000;
        font-weight: 700;
        padding: 1rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(247, 200, 0, 0.25);
      }
      
      .features {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
        gap: 2rem;
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 0 auto 5rem;
        padding: 0 clamp(1.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      }
      .feature-card {
        background: var(--bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 2rem;
        border-radius: var(--radius);
      }
      .feature-card h3 {
        font-family: "Bebas Neue", sans-serif;
        font-size: 1.8rem;
        color: var(--gold);
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }
      .feature-card p {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <path d="M20.57 14.86L22 13.43 20.57 12 17 15.57 8.43 7 12 3.43 10.57 2 9.14 3.43 7.71 2 5.57 4.14 4.14 2.71 2.71 4.14l1.43 1.43L2 7.71l1.43 1.43L2 10.57 3.43 12 7 8.43 15.57 17 12 20.57 13.43 22l1.43-1.43L16.29 22l2.14-2.14 1.43 1.43 1.43-1.43-1.43-1.43L22 16.29z"></path>
        </svg>
        BuffBook
      </a>
      <a href="/" class="btn-primary" style="padding: 0.5rem 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem;">Back to Book</a>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
      <p class="hero-eyebrow">Personalized Programming</p>
      <h1>Hand-crafted <span>Just For You.</span></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        No AI. No cookie-cutter templates. You fill out a comprehensive assessment, and I personally build your ideal hypertrophy plan from scratch in 72-96 hours.
      </p>
      <a href="/custom-plans/apply" class="btn-primary">Get Your Plan — 30 EUR</a>
    </section>

    <section class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>100% Custom</h3>
        <p>Built completely from scratch based on your weak points, injuries, and available equipment.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Science-Backed</h3>
        <p>Uses the exact peer-reviewed principles outlined in the BuffBook.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>Complete Guide</h3>
        <p>Delivered as a detailed PDF including warm-ups, progression schemes, and logging instructions.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
